text: Zakaria El Wardi (; born 17 August 1998) is a Moroccan footballer currently playing for Raja Casablanca as a midfielder. ==References== Category:Moroccan footballers Category:Moghreb Tétouan players Category:Raja Casablanca players Category:Living people Category:People from Tétouan Category:1998 births Category:Association football midfielders
